#!perl -w
use strict;

=head1 NAME

translate_seq - translates a sequence

=head1 SYNOPSIS

translate_seq E<lt> cdna_cds.fa E<gt> protein.fa

=head1 DESCRIPTION 

The script will translate one fasta file (on stdin) to protein on stdout

